query: WITH entities AS (SELECT activity, authentication_id, id FROM core_customers WHERE ((activity = $1) AND ((authentication_id IS NOT DISTINCT FROM $4) AND COALESCE(id > $3, true) OR COALESCE(authentication_id > $4, authentication_id IS NOT NULL))) ORDER BY authentication_id ASC NULLS FIRST, id ASC LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: CustomerId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.authentication_id asc nulls first, i.id asc, i.id, e.sequence
